<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Promotions and advertising of new technologies are presented in such a way that they are valuable and necessary. At the same time, technology has a downside impact on people as we progress, not only on our lifespan has become short but also they carry risks on our overall health with the addition of technology.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>So without any further delay, Let’s get to know the 11 most important disadvantages of technology.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

